data.title: Japan dairy giant Megmilk Snow Brand to establish Vietnam subsidiary
data.meta_description: Japan's leading diary maker Megmilk Snow Brand will establish a Vietnamese subsidiary with charter capital of VND265 billion ($10.4 million) this September.
